# Folder-local AGENTS.md template

Copy this to a source folder that has non-obvious constraints. Keep 10-30 lines total. Delete sections that have no content; do not leave empty headers.

```markdown
## Purpose

1-2 lines describing what this folder owns. No background, no "because".

## Notes

- Gotcha that bites agents.
- Constraint needing explanation.
- Decision not obvious from diff.
- Self-correction after human/build feedback.
```

Rules:
- No dates (git has them).
- No routine edits (obvious from diff).
- No redundancy with code, comments, or parent docs.
- Only durable facts not obvious from reading the code.
- 10-30 lines total. If you cannot stay under 30, the folder is doing too much; split it.